text: Bilal Irshad (born 1 February 1991) is a Pakistani cricketer. He made his first-class debut for Hyderabad in the 2010–11 Quaid-e-Azam Trophy on 22 November 2010. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Pakistani cricketers Category:Hyderabad (Pakistan) cricketers Category:Lahore Blues cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
